# Idol Manager Web - Phase 1 Implementation Rules

## Stack
- Vite + React + TypeScript
- Jotai for state management
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Framer Motion for animations
- Radix UI for accessible components

## File Structure
src/
  store/
    atoms.ts - Jotai atoms (bondLevel, personalityScore, etc.)
  components/
    StatsBar.tsx - Main stats dashboard
    BondLevelBar.tsx - Progress bar for bond level
    PersonalityGauge.tsx - Personality sliders
    StatChangeAnimation.tsx - Floating text animations
  types/
    index.ts - TypeScript types
  App.tsx
  main.tsx
  index.css

## Coding Conventions
- Use functional components with hooks
- TypeScript strict mode
- Tailwind for all styling
- Korean language for UI text
- Mobile-first responsive design
